snippet.title: Super Mario 3D World - Full Game Walkthrough (All Green Stars & Stamps)
snippet.description: A 100% Complete Walkthrough of Super Mario 3D World for the Nintendo Wii U. This video shows off all 12 Worlds, all Green Stars, all Stamps and all Captain Toad Levels.
